\begin_layout Standard
By this time, 1h 55 minutes after introducing the ink, the ink from the
 second and third tube have reached the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

extraction canal
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

.
 The flow lines lower in the model lag behind due to the lower velocities
 there.
 Notice that the water level in the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

canal
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 at 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

