\begin_layout Section
Numerically modeling Pennnink's laboratory model
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Nowadays, modeling the flow in and streamlines in the Pennink's lab model
 is more or less straightforward.
 It can be done with the widely used groundwater model Modflow made publicly
 available by the USGS.
\end_layout

